<a name="bloodmoon"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Bloodmoon</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/1h_slash.shtml">1H Slash</a><BR>
Damage per second - 13.21<BR>
Damage 18 - Delay 28<BR>
Weight: 3.0 - DEF, ERU, HUM<BR>
Classes: <a href="/shadow_knight/weapons/1h_slash.shtml">SHD</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(STR +10) </font>
<BR>
Dropped in Plane of Hate.<BR>

